{
  "stem": "3449.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in a sleigh.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I think it was winter '45.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "February, January, February-- something like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Early '45.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now that's another story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I hope the tape doesn't run out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were hiding on a-- in an attic of the farm, there were-- of the barn.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were cows on the bottom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was an attic above, and we had a ladder.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We would climb up and hide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I sort of-- he made us a spot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then he found out-- when this farmer, that they kept Jews-- as I told you-- two farms that he found out that they were completely burned to the ground and killed, he started to really get frightened.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And since he decided not to [INAUDIBLE], not to let us go, didn't throw us out-- after that little meeting, about a month later.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And every time the-- the signal came around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was some Germans driving by.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Ukrainians are looking around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Right away we ran.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He took the ladder away from the farm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He hid us in the-- [INAUDIBLE] well, we knew how to get into-- into that corner of the stack of the hay in the farm.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyhow, four weeks after he decided to let us stay, we knew he was doing something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somehow we-- we heard him working in the barn, downstairs where the cows are.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know what he was doing, because he always worked at night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we trusted him explicitly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we weren't worried about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But why?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What's he doing?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One day he says to us, I have a present for you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So my father said, what is it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He says, surprise.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Come on.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we all crawled down from the farm-- from the barn.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
